    fun `Issue 1324 - Given a non-nullable function type variable with wrapped parameters then no unnecessary newline error should be reported`() {
        // A function type (not wrapped in nullable type) with its parameters on separate lines
        // should NOT report "Unnecessary newline before "("" error.
